One (1) board-certified pediatric surgeon, to be selected by the secretary;
One (1) board-certified pediatrician specializing in medical genetics, to be selected by the secretary;
One (1) perinatal social worker, to be selected by the secretary; and
One (1) representative from a non-university hospital with a Level II or a Level III NICU, selected by the secretary.
